article_title: 100-year business: R.W. Troxell evolves with insurance world

article_metadata.description: The Affordable Care Act continues to be a contentious issue with much uncertainty on how it will impact society. Private insurance companies are among those maneuvering to respond to the landmark legislation.R.W. Troxell, an independent agency headquartered in Springfield, sees it as another opportunity to demonstrate its value to the community.Twenty-five years ago, we weren’t very active in the life and health arena, but now it’s a big part of our business.
